 <div class="story">  <p>Dunetops is a town house community situated on a high ridge on the west side of Rte 158 in Kitty Hawk. The community shares a pool and some of the units have some ocean views off in the distance. Dunetops town houses can be found across the street from <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/woodard-acres.asp" title="Woodard Acres">Woodard Acres</a> and next to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/ocean-winds.asp" title="Ocean Winds">Ocean Winds</a> condominiums. </p>
